namespace pdg { /**

\fn pdg::Serializer::serialize_3u

\brief serialize 3 unsigned bytes

Write a three byte value in the range of **0 to 16,777,216** into the data stream. 

\warning if the value is outside the range then only the info from the least significant three bytes will be written into the serialized data stream.

\note data size: 3 bytes

\remark there is no serialize_3(signed int); use serialize_4 instead

\sa Deserializer.deserialize_3u

**/ }